INSERT INTO `th_news` VALUES ('653', 'Mr.Axel Brugmann, general manager of ATEK, Germany, has trained in detail for all sales engineers', 'Lang an science and technology', '../uploads/20161031/20161031114431_839.jpg', '', '0', '', '2', '0', '<p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">The company is currently in strategic partnership with French ControlSys, German FAG, SKF, IAMT and NOVOTEST companies to provide efficient and reliable test benches for domestic manufacturers of automotive parts, greases, bearings and railway equipment. The company&#39;s goal is not only to provide excellent products, pay more attention to a full range of services, not only to product services, more importantly, the introduction and promotion of methods, I hope to be able to contribute to China&#39;s scientific research undertakings.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">In the field of industrial services, the company has noticed that there is a huge gap in the field of domestic industrial outsourcing services, and extremely lack of excellent large-scale test equipment. Because the company is still in its development stage, it is not realistic to purchase large expensive test equipment in large quantities. To solve this problem, the company collaborate with outstanding outsourcing service providers abroad. At present, there has been a cooperation agreement with Schaeffler on the testing of grease and other samples.</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;">Since its inceptio