INSERT INTO `th_news` VALUES ('606', 'Enterprise culture', '', '', '', '1', '', '70', '0', '<p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Company Policy】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Making the Profits, Returning the investment to the shareholders;&nbsp;Contributing to the society, Offering welfare for the employees</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Business Mission】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;">Pursuing the goal without limit, Creating the future</span><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </span></span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Value Concept】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Start from profits making, motivate from value creating</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Working Goal】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">The foundation of daily work is to exploring the customers resource deeply, the working flow is cooperation and interaction; Longen focuses on cost saving, profit maximizing, excellent service, a win-win situation for all together is the goal.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Teambuilding Concept】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Develop within one voice, Spare no efforts, Mutual trust, Risk sharing</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;Longen initiates the leading role strategy. Everyone shall be loyal to the team, brave to bear the responsibilities, realize the potential abilities, dedicated to the work engaged. Everyone needs to strive to be the pacemaker in the team, shall be mutual trust &amp; close cooperation for the united mission. In the serious competition, Longen spare no efforts to overcome the hardship &amp; realize the company strategy and employees could make the personal value come true at the same time.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Innovation Belief】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Sustainable innovation, Tolerant of failure</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Sustainable innovation is the power and origin of the Longen growth. Rich innovative atmosphere needs to be created, Longen always support the innovation from the staffs, in terms of innovated technology, innovated management, innovated principle &amp; environment. Longen could understand &amp; tolerate and even encourage the failures in the innovations. Longen set the innovation to be the quality, philosophy &amp; prevailing custom.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Manpower Philosophy】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Manpower adapt to the position, Position fit for the manpower</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">As far as the manpower is willing to work actively, and they will be &nbsp;the talents what Longen need. Longen always select the talents who could fit for the position &amp; the knowledge reserve they have. To optimize the above 2 factors combination. To maximize the abilities and expertise of all staffs.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Quality Belief】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Higher standard with precision &amp; zero defect</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Longen fundamental requirements for the staffs are higher standard with precision and zero defect. It is the attitude what the staffs shall have. Higher standard is the precondition, precision is the essential request and zero defect is the ultimate goal. Three factors are linked mutually and they are indispensable.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Sales &amp; Marketing Philosophy】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Creating value for the customers &amp; winning friends for Longen.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">In 21st Century, the slogan “create the value for the customers” do not mean the simple sell &amp; purchase relationship, and in the present it aims to realize the value what the customers could not earned or even they could not get. The goal is to make the customers to be sustainable one and finally convert the customers to be the friends of Longen.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">【Safety Concept】</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Priceless Life &amp; Safety First</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Life is the only once, life needs to be respected &amp; cherished. Safety is the first, &amp; prevention is the main. Safety is the fundamental need and request in the business activities. As long as the life &amp; safety of the staffs could be secured when the machines and equipments are in normal function of Longen could realize sustainable,healthy &amp; harmonized growth.</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '380', '2016-10-24', '', '', '', 'info', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '1574062124', '0', '', '', '', '1', '', '', '', '');
