INSERT INTO `tp_archives` VALUES ('633', '热烈庆祝朗安科技成立10周年！', '', '从今天回望过去，2011年9月30日，在这平凡的一天，我们梦想的种子终于发芽。有了开始，便坚定了执着与信念。3650天，我们携手并肩，风雨同舟。', '1', 'NULL', '', '', '', '', '20211014\c9c4f84aa16c5fcb6793731a50a8289a.jpg', '', '152', '<table align="center"><tbody><tr class="firstRow"><td width="608" valign="top"><br/></td><td width="608" valign="top" style="word-break: break-all;" align="left"><p><img src="/lakj/kbcms/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211014/1634194249345502.png" title="1634194249345502.png" alt="蓝线.png"/><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " helvetica="" pingfang="" hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" yahei="" letter-spacing:="" text-align:="" background-color:="">&nbsp; 从今天回望过去，2011年9月30日，在这平凡的一天，我们梦想的种子终于发芽。有了开始，便坚定了执着与信念。3650天，我们携手并肩，风雨同舟。一路走来，从几个人的团队到近百人的大家庭，从寥寥无几的订单到销量满载，我们始终没有放弃最初的梦想，奋斗一直在路上。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " helvetica="" pingfang="" hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" yahei="" text-align:="" background-color:="" letter-spacing:="" overflow-wrap:="" break-word="">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/lakj/kbcms/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211014/1634197191135791.jpg" title="1634197191135791.jpg" alt="1634197191135791.jpg" width="500" height="229" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 500px; height: 229px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; 10年间，我们感激每一位同事，没有你们的兢兢业业，没有你们的挥洒汗水，也就没有公司如今的成就。当每个人都撸起袖子坚守在自己岗位的时候，公司才有了由内而外的自信。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 3em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我们感激每一次挑战和机遇，面对坎坷和挑战，我们毅然选择直面，从无到有，从有到精。坦然无畏，成就日后开疆拓土；稳扎稳打，终筑壁垒。<span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 3em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我们感激每一位客户的信任，是你们的信任让我们走的更远，让我们不断创新，不断前行。十年依旧，感恩一路有你们。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " helvetica="" pingfang="" hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" yahei="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" text-align:="" white-space:="" background-color:="" line-height:="" overflow-wrap:="" break-word=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/lakj/kbcms/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211014/1634196438619313.jpg" title="1634196438619313.jpg" alt="1634196438619313.jpg" width="500" height="329" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 500px; height: 329px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/lakj/kbcms/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211014/1634196455654556.png" title="1634196455654556.png" alt="1634196455654556.png" width="500" height="614" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 500px; height: 614px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/lakj/kbcms/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211014/1634196497106370.png" title="1634196497106370.png" alt="1634196497106370.png" width="500" height="392" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 500px; height: 392px;"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/lakj/kbcms/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211014/1634196537920751.png" title="1634196537920751.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " helvetica="" pingfang="" hiragino="" sans="" microsoft="" yahei="" font-size:="" letter-spacing:="" white-space:="" background-color:="" text-align:="" line-height:="" overflow-wrap:="" break-word=""><br/></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 3em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;十年耕耘，十年收获。</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 3em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-wo